Philips represents and warrants to Customer that all Products delivered and any services provided hereunder:
i. conform to the Specifications on the Delivery Date [Redacted - Commercially Sensitive];
ii. unless otherwise agreed with Customer in writing, are new (do not contain any used or reconditioned parts or materials) and fit for the purposes for which they are intended;
iii. are of sound workmanship, good quality and free from defects in construction, manufacture and material [Redacted - Commercially Sensitive];
iv. the manufacturing and shipment of the Product comply in all respects with applicable Laws, regulations, certification requirements, including health and safety standards and all other applicable regulatory requirements for the manufacture and shipment of Products;
v. are free and clear of all liens, encumbrances, and other Claims against title; and
vii. comply in all respects with the terms of this Agreement and the applicable Purchase Orders.

